Disk inlet
==========

Demonstrates the syntheticTurbulenceInlet on a circular disk inlet
with a constant area-averaged mean speed (Umean = 10 m/s).

Geometry            Disk (two-block O-grid).
Inlet target        Umean = 10 m/s.
Friction velocity   Auto-computed from the bulk Reynolds number.
Solver              foamRun, incompressibleFluid.

Run with:           ./Allrun
Clean with:         ./Allclean

Notes
-----
Coarse mesh sized for a quick tutorial run. Refine the mesh and extend
endTime in system/controlDict to develop converged turbulence statistics.
